The eat in kitchen and island overlook the large combination family & dining room. The master suite includes an oversized bathroom, his & her sinks and walk-in closet. Enjoy the community cabana, resort style community pool, tot lot, community park areas, and maintenance of common areas. All of these amenities are INCLUDED in the HOA.
